data.description: Welcome to this stunning lakeside retreat! This charming home is complete with a warm and inviting fireplace in the living room. With three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a two-car garage. Granite counter tops and wood flooring to complete the feel. Upstairs, discover a versatile bonus room, ready to adapt to your needs. Step outside to the expansive back deck, the perfect setting for all your entertaining needs. Enjoy the outdoor seating area, complete with its own fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance for gatherings. In addition to this exceptional home, you’ll find a 40x60 shop that includes a wood-burning fireplace, custom floor coating, and large overhead doors, providing full ceiling access, making it ideal for your RV and lake toys. There’s even a separate she-shed or man-cave for your personal hideaway. This remarkable property is nestled within a wooded lot, offering a serene and picturesque setting, all conveniently located less than a mile from the lake with easy access to a marina. As a bonus, an additional parcel is included.
